    "He entered Harvard in 1914.": [],
    "Among his classmates and friends was the future author John Dos Passos (1896-1970).": [],
    "The two remained close their entire lives.": [],
    "They wrote for the <em>Harvard Monthly</em>, the undergraduate magazine.": [],
    "McComb and Dos Passos toured Europe before McComb graduated from Harvard in 1918.": [
