    "He began working on his M. A. at Harvard.": [],
    "He married Constance Atwood in 1923.": [],
    "In 1924 he published an article in the magazine jointly published by Princeton and Harvard, <em>Art Studies</em>, \"The Life and Times of Francesco di Giorgio.\"": [
