    "Among his students included the future Harvard art historian <a href=\"/freedbergs\">Sydney Joseph Freedberg</a>.": [],
    "In the 1930s, McComb adopted a pro-Fascist attitude toward Franco and Mussolini (thought not Hitler), which caused tension with many, included Dos Passos.": [
